  • PLAYREADY_POLICY_NOT_FOUND - PlayReady policy not found for entry [@ENTRY_ID@].
  • PLAYREADY_PROFILE_NOT_FOUND - PlayReady profile configuration not found
  • PLAYREADY_POLICY_OBJECT_NOT_FOUND - PlayReady policy object with id [@POLICY_ID@] not found.
  • KEY_ID_DONT_MATCH - Input key ID [@KEY_ID@] doesn't match entry key ID [@ENTRY_KEY_ID@]
  • ANALOG_OUTPUT_PROTECTION_ID_NOT_ALLOWED - Analog video output protection ID [@ID_1@] maybe specified only if ID [@ID_2@] is not specified.
  • COPY_ENABLER_TYPE_MISSING - At least one copy enabler type should be specified
  • FAILED_TO_GET_ENTRY_KEY_ID - Failed to get PlayReady key id for entry [@ENTRY_ID@].
  • DRM_DEVICE_NOT_SUPPORTED - DRM DEVICE "@DRM_DEVICE_TYPE@" is not supported
  • INTEGRATION_DISPATCH_FAILED - Dispatching integration type [@TYPE@] failed
  • INTEGRATION_NOTIFY_FAILED - Notifying failed
  • BUSINESS_PROCESS_SERVER_NOT_FOUND - Business-Process server id [@ID@] not found
  • BUSINESS_PROCESS_SERVER_DUPLICATE_SYSTEM_NAME - Business-Process server with system name [@NAME@] already exists.
  • BUSINESS_PROCESS_CASE_NOT_FOUND - No business-process case found.
  • PROVIDED_ENTRY_IS_ALREADY_A_QUIZ - Provided entry [@ENTRY_ID@] is already a quiz
  • PROVIDED_ENTRY_IS_NOT_A_QUIZ - Provided entry [@ENTRY_ID@] is not a quiz
  • PARENT_ID_IS_MISSING - Parent ID is missing
  • WRONG_PARENT_TYPE - Parent cue point id [@ENTRY_ID@] has the wrong type
  • ANSWER_UPDATE_IS_NOT_ALLOWED - Answer update is not allowed for quiz [@ENTRY_ID@]
  • USER_ENTRY_QUIZ_ALREADY_SUBMITTED - The user-entry-quiz id is already submitted, answers cannot be added/updated
  • ENTRY_ID_NOT_GIVEN - No entry id given
  • NO_SUCH_FILE_TYPE - Document cannot be provided. No such file type
  • QUIZ_CANNOT_BE_DOWNLOAD - Quiz cannot be download
  • QUIZ_USER_ENTRY_ALREADY_EXISTS - A quiz user-entry for the given user-id and entry-id [@ENTRY_ID@] already exists, cannot create duplicate
  • INVALID_SCHEDULE_END_BEFORE_START - End time [@END@] must be after start time [@START@]
  • MAX_SCHEDULE_DURATION_REACHED - Maximum schedule duration [@MAX@] reached
  • MAX_SCHEDULE_DURATION_MUST_MATCH_END_TIME - Duration must match end time, keep one of them null to calculate automatically
  • RECURRENCE_CANT_BE_DELETE - Recurence [@ID@] cannot be deleted, use cancel or delete the parent recurring event [@PARENT_ID@]
  • SCHEDULE_EVENT_TYPE_CANT_BE_UPDATED - Can't update from type [@SOURCE_TYPE@] to type [@TARGET_TYPE@]
